room_title: Escape room "Mystery Mansion" by Breakout Games - Jacksonville in Jacksonville
review: I took my son and his friends here for his birthday party and they had so much fun!  Our game master was Preston and he was great.  The lady that greeted us at the entrance was also pleasant and kind.  I would recommend this establishment.  Thanks!

room_title: Escape room "Mystery Mansion" by Breakout Games - Jacksonville in Jacksonville
review: This is a great place to go for team building! The game master gets your team excited for the adventure and encourages your progress. I'll definitely go again with friends and family!

room_title: Escape room "Mystery Mansion" by Breakout Games - Jacksonville in Jacksonville
review: Great fun! First time doing one of these as a Christmas gift and it was way better than I could have expected. Our game master Isabelle was a true professional and made our experience that much better. Will definitely be coming back.

room_title: Escape room "Mystery Mansion" by Breakout Games - Jacksonville in Jacksonville
review: This was a FANTASTIC escape room. My wife and I have done more than a dozen across several states, and this easily one of the best we've encountered. Definitely looking forward to booking our next escape.

room_title: Escape room "Mystery Mansion" by Breakout Games - Jacksonville in Jacksonville
review: Went to breakout games and had tons of fun with a group of six.  We did the Haunted Mansion murder mystery room and made it out! Our guide Brent was super helpful and nice and we enjoyed our time here.
